sense.gloss: previous generation (e.g. one's parents), family predecessor

meanings: counter for decades of ages, eras, etc.

sdata.j: |↑先代|↑↓せんだい↓はいつでもにこにこしている↑人↑↓ひと↓だったけど、↑今度↑↓こんど↓のはどうもお↑天気↑↓てんき↓↑屋↑↓や↓でいかんね。
sdata.e: The previous boss smiled all the time, but the current boss has somehow become moody.
